$interpreted: : Five days later...
Sennosuke: So many people are here to see the competition!
Sennosuke: Master, is that the objective?
Kaito: Yes. Grab that sign and you've won.
Sennosuke: Master, there's someone over there selling your favorite dango. I'll go get us some!
Kaito: The competition's about to start. I won't have time to eat it.
Kaito: Here, you go buy some to eat while you watch. I'll get some after the match.
Sennosuke: Okay! Imma eat ten of 'em!
Yan-Bo: We cross paths as drifting clouds, competing for the prize in this fabled arena.
Yan-Bo: So you've come. I look forward to learning from you.
Kaito: ...Hmm, as do I.
Yan-Bo: And your companion's here, too. I didn't have time last time to greet your...?
Kaito: He's my disciple, Sennosuke.
Yan-Bo: Greetings.
Sennosuke: ……
Yan-Bo: ...Kaito! I heard someone say that day that you were once a member of the Secret Society.
Yan-Bo: Excuse my bluntness, but I'm very curious. Why did you leave?
Kaito: I couldn't stand their deceitful ways. That's all. It was nothing dramatic.
Kaito: We should let them know we've arrived.
Yan-Bo: I'm sorry, I shouldn't have asked.
Kaito: Not at all. I'll be going now.
Sennosuke: Master! Getting out of the Secret Society was obviously a big deal! I wanna know what happened, too!
Kaito: It's all in the past, there's nothing much to say now. Just remember not to let them tangle themselves up with you.
Kaito: ...Once they've pulled you in, you'll never get clean of them.
Sennosuke: No problem, Master, I'm happy just the way things are already! Everything's been so great with you!
Kaito: ...Yes, we're doing just fine.
Edensnatch Manager: All participants please sign in! Audience, please take your seats!
Kaito: I should go.
Sennosuke: Go, Master, go!
Kaito: Sennosuke.
Sennosuke: Master?
Kaito: When I win, we'll go have a feast. I'll tell you all about what happened once the time comes.
Sennosuke: Damn, I had to line up for so long just to get this dango... Where's Master got to now?
Yan-Bo: Your talents are admirable.
Kaito: Yours are strong, too. No wonder they say you're talented.
Yan-Bo: If I win today, what say you join my school and study martial arts with me?
Kaito: ...Why are you so determined to found your own school?
Yan-Bo: I want my martial skills, my legacy, to live on. To do that, I must have my own school and disciples.
Kaito: What's that got to do with the Edensnatch?
Yan-Bo: The Edensnatch will prove my strength, my worthiness to be a sage and found my own lineage.
Kaito: ...I see. But the competition's not over yet. We'll see who wins!
Kaito: (It's so slippery! What is this!?)
Yan-Bo: Take this!
Kaito: Wait!
Yan-Bo: I win!
Yan-Bo: (Grease!?)
Kaito: (Who put grease on the pole...!? It must've been them...!)
Kaito: You slippery dodgers!!
Sennosuke: Master!!!
Sennosuke: Hold on, Master! I'll get you to the medic!
Kaito: Sennosuke... Get to the Alliance... Yan-Bo... cheated...
Sennosuke: Master, Master...!!!
Sennosuke: Yan-Bo—
Yan-Bo: What...
Sennosuke: Give me back my Master!
Alliance Guard: What are you doing? No mucking about in the arena!
Alliance Guard: You pesky little hoodlum, scram!
Sennosuke: Let go of me!! Master can't drop dead just like that!! You've killed him with your trickery, Yan-Bo...!
Meddlesome Spectator: Hey, he just accused Yan-Bo of cheating...
Panicked Spectator: Huh? Why would Yan-Bo need to cheat? Besides, the Edensnatch's always been dangerous, death's never been an impossibility!
Edensnatch Manager: Quiet!
Yan-Bo: Wait a moment, I just...
Edensnatch Manager: The Edensnatch is over. Yan-Bo of the Capybara Tribe is victorious! Congratulations, you've qualified to enter the Martial Arts Tourney!
Yan-Bo: Wait, I...
Edensnatch Manager: Thanks to you all for attending today! Everybody give Yan-Bo a big round of applause!
Edensnatch Manager: And everybody please give our Capybara Tribe Tinctures a try! You can take a few bottles with you when you leave to show your support for Yan-Bo!
Yan-Bo: ...What!?
Sennosuke: Yan-Bo...! You lousy, rotten scoundrel!!
Edensnatch Manager: What are you letting him make havoc in here for? After him!
Yan-Bo: But...
Edensnatch Manager: W-what? Is it about the tincture?
Yan-Bo: Enough with your tinctures. I think there was something wrong with Kaito's reaction... I stepped in some grease by the pole just a moment ago...
Edensnatch Manager: ...What!? Grease, where?
Yan-Bo: The pole that Kaito fell from. I was going to grab him, but stepped on something slippery and missed him...
Edensnatch Manager: Grease!? How could that be, we haven't done anything to make it more difficult!
Yan-Bo: Somebody could have put grease on the pole if they wanted to harm him. The implications of this are hugely consequential. Should I go take a look?
Edensnatch Manager: ...No! You're both a participant and a witness, Yan-Bo. Don't do anything rash, or you'll come under suspicion! And don't go anywhere, neither!
Yan-Bo: ...Okay, you're right. But please, hurry up and get to the bottom of this!
Edensnatch Manager: I will... This is no laughing matter. I'd best tell the Chieftain! I'll be right there!
